Gaupol 0.25.1
=============

 [X] Use Gtk.render_layout instead of deprecated Gtk.paint_layout to
     render line length margin in text views
 [X] Add GTK+ to list of dependencies in the README file (GTK+ has
     always been a dependency, its explicit mention was just forgotten
     when migrating from PyGTK to PyGObject)

